296
00:11:32,286 --> 00:11:34,286
When they did another ultrasound

297
00:11:34,288 --> 00:11:35,287
a few weeks later,

298
00:11:35,289 --> 00:11:37,389
they discovered that

299
00:11:37,391 --> 00:11:41,793
I had re-sorbed
the other fetus.

300
00:11:41,795 --> 00:11:44,096
Do I regret this?
No.

301
00:11:44,098 --> 00:11:46,531
I believe his tissue
has made me stronger.

302
00:11:46,533 --> 00:11:48,734
I now have the strength
of a grown man

303
00:11:48,736 --> 00:11:50,836
and a little baby.

304
00:11:50,838 --> 00:11:53,338
Okay, why don't you
throw the ball to somebody else?

305
00:11:53,340 --> 00:11:54,473
Nope.

306
00:11:54,475 --> 00:11:56,575
Oh, yes, Stanley,
Come on, your turn.

307
00:11:56,577 --> 00:11:58,009
- You have to go.
- I will not!

308
00:11:58,011 --> 00:12:00,078
Okay...

309
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:01,346
I'm going to

310
00:12:01,348 --> 00:12:02,681
toss the ball

